						               													<description>After centuries of machinations, Hades finally defeated the other gods. He is about to drag mankind into the underworld to reign supreme. Only the wise old Daedalus, inventor of genius, still stands against him, helped by a handful of heroes. But these will not cooperate: only one will be the savior of humanity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Hades Trap is played on a modular board made up of 9 tiles, which allows you to renew your games. Each player plays as a hero who will be able to perform a variable number of actions in turn. You will be able to move around or interact with the square on which you are standing, in order to fight skeletons, activate mechanisms or even knock out your opponents! But beware, if you step on a breadcrumb trail, the Minotaur will be alerted and will run in the direction of its patrol! Maybe this is your chance to pull it towards your enemies?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Collect three of the available medallions and exit the labyrinth to be declared the winner. The medallions can be retrieved in many ways, so you'll need to be resourceful and brave to complete this important quest.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
